# TaskFlow Environment Configuration
# ==================================
# This is a client-only Angular application.
# No environment variables are required for development or production builds.
#
# Data Persistence:
#   All task data is stored in the browser's localStorage.
#   No external database or API connection is needed.
#
# Deployment:
#   This app is configured for static deployment on Vercel.
#   Simply connect your repository to Vercel and it will auto-detect
#   the Angular build configuration.
#
# Optional Configuration:
#   If you extend this app with a backend API in the future,
#   add your variables below and reference them in
#   src/environments/environment.ts and
#   src/environments/environment.prod.ts
#
# Example (not currently used):
# API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api